ertrag und Arbeitskampf, Mitbestimmung im Betrieb und Unternehmen).  aThis textbook offers a systematic presentation and discussion of the basic principles and features of labor and employment law. It highlights the structures and trends and clarifies their relevance to conflict resolution.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 21. Jun 2021) 0aLabor laws and legislationzGermany. 4aArbeitsrecht. 7aLAW / Labor & Employment.2bisacsh  aLabor Law.1 aBieder, Marcus, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus DeG Package 2020 Part 1z978311069627108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2019z9783110664232oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Law 2019z9783110606249oZDB-23-DGC0 cEPUBz97831103886260 cprintz978311028581940uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311028582640uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110285826423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783110285826.jpg  a978-3-11-069627-1  DG Plus DeG Package 2020 Part 1b2020  aEBA_CL_LAEC  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGCb2019  aZDB-23-DGGb2019